author: @sarahb4484
content:
This is my hometown I grew up in that neighborhood. In the 90s and early 2000s we had many Free concerts the largest before Madonna I guess was Rolling Stones and Lenny kravitz which The Rolling Stones I missed but Lenny was awesome!
She will have good time and the public will be very reciprocated towards her. Brazilians love to sing along with the musicians…
